  "title": "🦅 Events ambassador",
  "description": "<p>At Euphoria Organisation we believe that its our people that makes &amp; creates us. We focus on personal and business development of each and every of our team member. We help multinational companies build and increase thier brand awareness as well as revenue through person to person interactions.</p>\n<p>Here's what you'll be engaged in...</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Engage with clients &amp; customers</li>\n  <li>Collaborating closely with major clients to develop solutions and strategies for their target audience</li>\n  <li>Develop team leadership skills to coach and drive standards</li>\n  <li>Improve client's branding and achiveing sales target</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Driven individuals with a great learning attitude</li>\n  <li>Good work initiative and excellent team players</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Coaching and 1-on-1 guidance provided along the way. Entry level welcome</li>\n  <li>Vibrant and collaborative team environment</li>\n  <li>Overseas exposure opportunities and international development workshops</li>\n  <li>Clear-cut advancement structure</li>\n</ul>",
